 das Stück und filme Dich dabei (beispielsweise mit Deinem Smartphone oder Deiner GoPro). Spiele zu einem Metronom und achte auf den richtigen Takt.'),(41098,3842,'_to_do_list_1_enumeration','field_5ad59dd1cbdfd'),(41099,3842,'to_do_list_2_enumeration','Bist Du zufrieden mit Deinem Video? Prima, dann lade das Video in einem der gängigen Video-Formate in unserem Uploader am Ende der Seite, hoch. Wir sind gespannt auf Deine Einspielung!'),(41100,3842,'_to_do_list_2_enumeration','field_5ad59dd1cbdfd'),(41101,3842,'to_do_list','3'),(41102,3842,'_to_do_list','field_5ad59d7ccbdfc'),(41103,3912,'bckgr-video',''),(41104,3912,'_bckgr-video','field_5abcbef18d20f'),(41105,3912,'image_table_0_image','3532'),(41106,3912,'_image_table_0_image','field_5abcdaa632ec2'),(41107,3912,'image_table_0_description','Information'),(41108,3912,'_image_table_0_description','field_5abcdadf32ec3'),(41109,3912,'image_table_1_image','3543'),(41110,3912,'_image_table_1_image','field_5abcdaa632ec2'),(41111,3912,'image_table_1_description','Notendownload'),(41112,3912,'_image_table_1_description','field_5abcdadf32ec3'),(41113,3912,'image_table_2_image','3533'),(41114,3912,'_image_table_2_image','field_5abcdaa632ec2'),(41115,3912,'image_table_2_description','Mediathek'),(41116,3912,'_image_table_2_description','field_5abcdadf32ec3'),(41117,3912,'image_table','3'),(41118,3912,'_image_table','field_5abcda6d32ec1'),(41119,3912,'table_content_0_image','3514'),(41120,3912,'_table_content_0_image','field_5abcf0495afba'),(41121,3912,'table_content_0_description','Flöten'),(41122,3912,'_table_content_0_description','field_5abcf0605afbb'),(41123,3912,'table_content_1_image','3502'),(41124,3912,'_table_content_1_image','field_5abcf0495afba'),(41125,3912,'table_content_1_description','Klarinetten'),(41126,3912,'_table_content_1_description','field_5abcf0605afbb'),(41127,3912,'table_content_2_image','3515'),(41128,3912,'_table_content_2_image','field_5abcf0495afba'),(41129,3912,'table_content_2_description','Obo